org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.tigr.contig

Interface TigrContigReadVisitor


  • public interface TigrContigReadVisitor
    TigrContigReadVisitor is a visitor interface to visit a single read inside contig from a TIGR .contig encoded file. The id, direction and valid range of the read have already been given by TigrContigVisitor.visitRead(String, long, org.jcvi.jillion.core.Direction, org.jcvi.jillion.core.Range).
    Author:
    dkatzel
